    <section class="container">

      <article class="post">
        <h1 class="post-title">Hey folks, I'm <a href="!!!" target="_blank" class="colorful">@jomrcr</a>.</h1>

        <p>I study <b class="colorful">mathematics</b> in the co-op program at the University of Waterloo. My focus is in combinatorics (counting things), optimization, statistics, and pure mathematics.</p>

        <p>In the Fall I'll be a <b class="colorful">data science</b> intern at Facebook in the South Bay. Previously I've interned as a program manager at Microsoft, a mobile developer at Noom, and as a <b class="colorful">web developer</b> at Tagged (ifwe), and Bazaarvoice.</p>

        <p>My studies and internships have taken me around the <b class="colorful">world</b>. I've studied abroad in Hong Kong, and worked in Seattle, NYC, SF, and Austin.</p>

        <div class="map-container">
          <span class="dot colorful seattle"></span>
          <span class="dot colorful waterloo"></span>
          <span class="dot colorful austin"></span>
          <span class="dot colorful sf"></span>
          <span class="dot colorful nyc"></span>
          <span class="dot colorful hk"></span>
          {{> map}}
        </div>

        <p>I love travelling to new places, trying new things, and making new friends.</p>

        <p>Come say <a href="!!!" target="_blank" class="colorful">hello</a> :)</p>

      </article>

    </section>

